    "Source: IRDB (codes/Epson/Unknown_ELPST12/131,85.csv) — MIT license.",
    "ELPST12 is a popular Epson remote shipped with many EB-S, EB-X, EB-W",
    "series classroom/business projectors. Smaller button set than the full",
    "business remote — limited to power/menu nav/source/mute/freeze.",
    "Uses NEC (not NEC2) — different wire bytes than the business preset",
    "even though IRDB lists the same device/subdevice.",
    "Stored as raw timing arrays — firmware lacks a named NEC2 path, raw fallback works.",
    "Carrier: 38 kHz. NEC pulse-distance: 9000/4500us header, 560us bit, 560us '0' space, 1690us '1' space."
